# ScreenReaderX

Advanced screen text reader using EasyOCR or Tesseract. Supports CLI with `screenreaderx readall`.

## Installation

```bash
pip install .
```

## Usage

```bash
screenreaderx readall --lang tur --engine easyocr --show
```
